description:
Much like the first nine seasons of the Roseanne sitcom, there is no satisfying end to this video.

There were many painful cuts in this video's contents, so if you were a fan of the show and are upset I didn't really go into deal about certain aspects of its nine season run, it was either because I didn't have time to fit them in or couldn't find anything interesting to say about them.

This video is probably best understood in the context of the second one I have planned in the future. It probably would have made more sense to just make that one, but I love long winded intros that set the stage. This video even has two of them.
